ZH: 必须遵守规定。
EN: It is necessary to follow the rules.

ZH: 他必须完成作业。
EN: He must finish his homework.

ZH: 这是必要的。
EN: This is essential.

ZH: 必胜无疑。
EN: Victory is assured.

ZH: 勇往直前是必要的。
EN: It is necessary to march forward bravely.

ZH: 他必然能成功。
EN: He is bound to succeed.

ZH: 我们每个人都必须尽力帮助别人。
EN: Each of us must do our best to help others.

ZH: 为了保护大自然，我们必须减少浪费。
EN: In order to protect nature, we must reduce waste.

ZH: 他必须向老师求助。
EN: He must seek help from the teacher.

ZH: 必胜利踏上胜利的大门。
EN: Victory steps towards the gate of victory.

ZH: 我们必须坚定地迈出第一步。
EN: We must take the first step firmly.

ZH: 为了成功，必须有耐心。
EN: Patience is necessary for success.

ZH: 要取得好成绩，必须认真学习。
EN: To achieve good grades, one must study diligently.

ZH: 他必须改变自己的态度。
EN: He must change his attitude.

ZH: 坚持锻炼必有所得。
EN: Persistence in exercise will yield results.

ZH: 要做家务，必克服懒惰。
EN: Overcoming laziness is necessary to do housework.

ZH: 必做好准备在未来。
EN: Be prepared for the future.

ZH: 为了成功，必须克服困难。
EN: To succeed, one must overcome difficulties.

ZH: 勤奋学习必有所成。
EN: Diligent study will definitely bring results.

ZH: 他们必须尽快采取行动。
EN: They must take action as soon as possible.
